name: Nazi Frankenstein / The story of a monster
description:
Humans always wanted to be better - faster, stronger, durable. But their own ethics usually interrupt the most brave and novatore researchers... Usually. And then Nazis came.

They gave carte blanche to the dark geniuses between their ranks - to create a super human.

But it seems geniuses were such an uncontrollable force - as their sick creation also. Not fully alive but too stubborn to be dead - this madman's creation escaped, leaving only death on it's path.

Where is it now? Maybe, died. Or maybe it's behind you?
